{"word":"G5461 - φωτίζω - phōtízō - fo-tid'-zo - Enlighten","slug":"G5461","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φωτίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>phōtízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>fo-tid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Enlighten"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C6;&#x03C9;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - pho&#x0304;tizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>fo-tid'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5457\">G5457</a>; to <i>shed rays</i>, that is, to <i>shine</i> or (transitively) to <i>brighten</i> up (literally or figuratively): - enlighten, illuminate, (bring to, give) light, make to see."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2017\">G2017</a>, <a href=\"#/G2020\">G2020</a>, <a href=\"#/G5457\">G5457</a>, <a href=\"#/G5458\">G5458</a>, <a href=\"#/G5459\">G5459</a>, <a href=\"#/G5460\">G5460</a>, <a href=\"#/G5462\">G5462</a>"}]}